Qgis:

1. add Vector Layer: trechos da Transcarioca em .GPX
2. select tracks/routes instead of point features
3. add Raster Layer
4. configure limits and pallette of Raster Layer 
5. New Print Layout
  5.1 Add Map
    5.1.1 Find the best scale to adjust your map to the moldure
  5.2 Add Legend
  5.3 Add North 
  5.4 Add scale bar
  5.5 Add title
  5.6 Add references
  5.7 Add GRIDS
      5.7.1 Draw Coordinates 
        5.7.1.1 Vertical Ascendent


ArcGis:

1. Go to GPX to Features tool
  1.2 Add GPX files one by one converting them into Features (.shp)
For Raster creatin and Map Layout: almost the same as Qgis

